      "id": "1037549298803545",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "Game is surprisingly good",
      "review_description": "I entered this game with a negative tone of thought thinking it was gonna be another \"gtag slop\" game. It felt like it at first but after playing around a little bit i figured out it actually had a unique movement system that i don't think ive seen anyone else do.\nAnother thing when i heard the game was gonna have gambling I was kind of turned off from trying it but after getting in and playing around Its actually surprisingly free to play. In the first session I leveled up my monkey bomb guy to level 40 and i didn't even pay anything the amount of currency you get for free and if you wanna pay is very surprising.",
      "date": 1781817365,
      "review_helpful_count": 26,
      "author_display_name": "hazmat_0_0",
      "author_alias": "hazmat_0_0",
      "developer_response": {
